OL,3,GUK weather for today and tomorrow
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain across
OL,6,Fthe south clearing this evening,
OL,7,Fallowing clearer spells to develop
OL,8,Fbehind. Further north it will stay
OL,9,Fwindy with blustery showers, with
OL,10,Fthese turning wintry over the higher
OL,11,Fground. A chilly night to come, with a
OL,12,Ftouch of frost.
OL,13,
OL,14,CMonday:FMorning showers will gradually
OL,15,Fease through the day, with the best of
OL,16,Fthe brightness in the south. A little
OL,17,Fless cold on Monday, especially as the
OL,18,Fbreeze begins to ease.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
